Package com.vincent.twoheaps

package com.vincent.twoheaps
This package contains the problem using two heaps
- Maximize Capital (Leetcode 502)
- Find the medium from a data stream (LeetCode 295)
- Sliding Window medium (LeetCode 480)
- Schedule Tasks on Minimum Machines (Same as the meeting room question)
- Meeting Room III (LeetCode 2402)
